{"tid":2158364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊明醉駕撞毁逾80年歷史石圍欄  重建料需25萬元","createTime":"2020-08-15T16:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T06:54:37.000Z","uid":184679,"like":615,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"1398665eb55d41e6837caa8bf75a5919ec96e58c","tid":2158364,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:15:36.000Z","msg":"無綫藝人楊明8月8日凌晨涉及醉酒駕駛，其平治私家車在馬己仙峽道鏟上路邊，令一段3米石圍欄損毀。「城西關注組」成員張朝敦一直研究香港石牆，他翻查政府憲報分析，估計受損石圍欄在30年代興建，至今逾80年歷史，「好彩有堅固石圍欄，先可以頂住楊生架車。」他認為，若當局有保留石塊，仍可修復舊貌。中科興業董事總經理潘焯鴻計算，若要重造3米石圍欄，料涉及25萬元，港府可向楊明索償...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200816/E6OZAE7EOZFVXBHEBLPLIUPDFU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200816%2FE6OZAE7EOZFVXBHEBLPLIUPDFU%2F&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9EL6bKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=49ddaf33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200816%2FE6OZAE7EOZFVXBHEBLPLIUPDFU%2F&h=4506e35b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200816/E6OZAE7EOZFVXBHEBLPLIUPDFU/</a>"},{"pid":"cb2245dc554af1778b69909b4f0063fb4a314f2c","tid":2158364,"uid":3976,"like":385,"dislike":2,"score":383,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:17:36.000Z","msg":"立會換地「煎」都問議員拎返， 今次唔係唔問楊明拎返下嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eddaab96521751cb3304b703f90918b8d01aa49","tid":2158364,"uid":28759,"like":301,"dislike":3,"score":298,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:20:59.000Z","msg":"楊明一個月賣唔賣到 25 萬蚊燉湯"},{"pid":"bead6fd8dc06390088ee73e9fb7417e5b4856a81","tid":2158364,"uid":271369,"like":163,"dislike":1,"score":162,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:21:02.000Z","msg":"人地拖鞋大把錢....25萬..散錢"},{"pid":"52a343ca4c2c02b2151f3ad01b5c814c42df5828","tid":2158364,"uid":198245,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"bead6fd8dc06390088ee73e9fb7417e5b4856a81","tid":2158364,"uid":271369,"like":163,"dislike":1,"score":162,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:21:02